Subject: [PATCH 4/5] bootloader: Use the boot partition to store the dtbs
 instead of dtbo

A dtbo partition was mandatory on Andorid-9, and now we have a boot
partition to store dtbs. So use it instead.

Signed-off-by: Roman Stratiienko <r.stratiienko@gmail.com>
